node.text:
Nestled on a lush lot in Barron Park, 993 Los Robles is a unique property that is the epitome of luxury modern design and construction innovation. The home features steel framing and built-in digital home automation throughout. Complete with a gym & sauna, theatre room, outdoor kitchen, and sunken patio - this property is a must-see. Head to @veevhomes to learn more.
